	CREATE TABLE onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk6566
	(
			//Define schema of table
			UserId          int, 
			Start           DateTime, 
			Region          string, 
			Query           string, 
			Duration        int, 
			Urls            string,

		PARTITIONED BY BUCKETS (UserId) HASH (Region) //Column to partition by
	);
	ALTER TABLE onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk6566 ADD IF NOT EXISTS PARTITION (1);
	DROP FUNCTION IF EXISTS onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk2928;

	//create table weblogs on space-delimited website log data
	CREATE FUNCTION onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk2928()
	RETURNS @result TABLE
	(
		s_date DateTime,
		s_time string,
		s_sitename string,
		cs_method string, 
		cs_uristem string,
		cs_uriquery string,
		s_port int,
		cs_username string, 
		c_ip string,
		cs_useragent string,
		cs_cookie string,
		cs_referer string, 
		cs_host string,
		sc_status int,
		sc_substatus int,
		sc_win32status int, 
		sc_bytes int,
		cs_bytes int,
		s_timetaken int
	)
	AS
	BEGIN

		@result = EXTRACT
			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,
			cs_uristem string,
			cs_uriquery string,
			s_port int,
			cs_username string,
			c_ip string,

			cs_bytes int,
			s_timetaken int
		FROM @"/Samples/Data/WebLog.log"
		USING Extractors.Text(delimiter:' ');

	RETURN;
	END;
	CREATE VIEW onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk3090 
	AS 
		SELECT * FROM 
		(
			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
		) 
	AS 
	T(a, b);
	CREATE PROCEDURE onesdk7674.dbo.onesdk6554()
	AS BEGIN

	  AS 
		SELECT * FROM

		)

	END;"
  }
}
